imdb.plot outline: Journalist and avid adventure traveler, Kinga Philipps, explores America's wild spaces through heart pounding activities beyond carefully marked and manicured trails. Watch her go kite surfing, bungee jumping and more while surrounded by the majestic, natural beauty of America's great outdoors in Travel Channel's The Wild Side with Kinga Philipps.
imdb.title: The Wild Side with Kinga Philipps
akas: The Wild Side with Kinga Philipps (United States)
